</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0029-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0029-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>The draft reads Troops.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0029-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0029-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>For Congresss policy on local defense, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0123&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-01-02-0123-fn-0002#GEWN-03-01-02-0123-fn-0002" class="document">GW to James Warren, 30 July 1775, n.2</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0029-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0029-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>The draft reads piratical.</p>

